{"tid":1849231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港嘅中資公司根本就係病毒溫床！","createTime":"2020-01-29T02:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T03:32:19.000Z","uid":168703,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bba0a3652ff1f72b65ac0c17d2a7c31ffcab9fbe","tid":1849231,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:48:36.000Z","msg":"大家都知中資公司請埋一大堆支那人喺香港做嘢，呢啲平時喺香港嘅支那人最鐘意就係過年放假番支那。<br />\n<br />\n正當醫生都話去完支那要自我隔離嘅時候，因為管理層同部分員工都係支那人嘅關係，根本就唔會搞work from home，照樣一堆坐完高鐵甚至去完武漢嘅支那人過完年就番香港，一樣去番工。<br />\n<br />\n要有效阻止病毒傳染，必須要逼去完支那境嘅人都自我隔離！逼中資公司暫時停工或者行work from home。<br />\n<br />\n推到中資狗睇到，手動轉。"},{"pid":"bb60e2298e2988f7f59326f40d53518e460b9c0c","tid":1849231,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"係所有大公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3f128c6c56c8e5572ce3bb9e2abb3db65f3693","tid":1849231,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69ea1c5119b2ff57eb1ccf706c3c8d8d335b9641","tid":1849231,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:54:25.000Z","msg":"已知央企back office表示跟政府work from home<br />\n其他中資仍有繼續工作"},{"pid":"b6120a2782dcba9b058f902241c20517664cca9d","tid":1849231,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=30b553eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />